Improved the game's data handling

Updated the database schema, added more robust testing, and created a quick reference guide for the API endpoints.  The database schema now includes a Mermaid ER Diagram and a detailed table of relationships.  The test plan now includes a risk assessment matrix and example automated tests.  The addendum file contains API endpoint documentation and cURL commands.

